                    						<img alt="" src="https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo400w/20200413-corona-climate-3x2.jpg" width="400" height="267" srcset="https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo400w/20200413-corona-climate-3x2.jpg 400w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo800w/20200413-corona-climate-3x2.jpg 800w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo1200w/20200413-corona-climate-3x2.jpg 1200w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo1600w/20200413-corona-climate-3x2.jpg 1600w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo2000w/20200413-corona-climate-3x2.jpg 2000w" sizes="(min-width: 1720px) 826px, (min-width: 780px) calc(46.09vw + 43px), (min-width: 600px) 59.38vw, 93.21vw"/>
					</div>
											<figcaption class="caption">Patients were quickly evacuated from Feather River Hospital as it burned during the Camp Fire in Paradise, California, on Nov. 8, 2018.
															<span class="credit">(Josh Edelson/AFP via Getty Images)</span>
													</figcaption>
									</figure>
            			
			<header class="article-header">

												<div class="series-header">
					<p class="series-title"><a href="https://www.propublica.org/series/coronavirus" aria-label="In the series: Coronavirus">Coronavirus</a></p>
									</div>
				
				<h2 class="hed">Climate Change Won’t Stop for the Coronavirus Pandemic</h2>
								<p class="dek">The next several months could bring hurricanes, floods and fire, on top of the pandemic currently raging through the country. How do you shelter in place during an evacuation?</p>
								<div class="metadata">
					<p class="byline">by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/abrahm-lustgarten">Abrahm Lustgarten</a></p>
					<time class="timestamp" datetime="2020-04-13EDT14:00">April 13, 2 p.m. EDT</time>
				</div>

								
